Output assets/demo.gif
Set FontSize 13
Set Width 750
Set Height 450
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 20

Type "purr init" Sleep 300ms Enter Sleep 800ms
Type "purr add ." Sleep 300ms Enter Sleep 800ms
Type "purr commit -m "
Type '"initial commit"'
Sleep 300ms Enter Sleep 800ms
Type "purr ls" Sleep 300ms Enter Sleep 1500ms
Type "purr help" Sleep 300ms Enter Sleep 2000ms
